'''EMAS CANADA''' is a [[Christian]] interdenominational [[non-governmental organization|non-governmental organization (NGO)]] providing charitable medical and dental care to under-serviced areas throughout the world.
EMAS was founded in 1948,<ref>{{cite web|title=EMAS Canada - About Us|url=http://www.emascanada.org/aboutus.htm|accessdate=7 May 2013}}</ref> the EMAS CANADA national office is located in [[Burlington, Ontario|Burlington]], [[Ontario]].
EMAS supports local healthcare endeavours/initiatives and sends medical, surgical and dental teams of healthcare professionals to assist in under-serviced areas overseas.
